## How to Add Nodes to the Tree

### For Regular Agents:
```bash
# Add progress nodes (color automatically inherited)
python3 tools/add_new_node.py <parent_file> "Node Name" "Content/Description" <relationship>

# Example relationships: is_progress_of, implements, tests, documents, etc.
```

### For Orchestrator Agents:
```bash
# Create subtask nodes with specific colors
python3 tools/add_new_node.py <parent> "Agent Name Task" "Task description" is_subtask_of --color <color>

# Available colors: green, blue, purple, red, orange, pink, cyan, magenta, indigo, teal, brown, navy, olive
```

